{"tid":654562,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好怕受傷，唔敢對愛情太投入","createTime":"2018-05-05T17:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T21:00:40.000Z","uid":185426,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d17c941370b8820316ccda2122a593c175d43179","tid":654562,"uid":185426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"天生無乜安全感，鍾意亂諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚越去投入一段感情，會跌得越痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣對我嘅另一半係咪好自私？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffcd15bfea93fb079fb0d9e84a853adf8e0eac7","tid":654562,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T17:56:52.000Z","msg":"受過傷，所以驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9b1fcd4565e1d71de86c6aff777a452b20d133","tid":654562,"uid":123657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T17:59:09.000Z","msg":"跌過痛過就會怕，人心難測"},{"pid":"724db500166326d502b34a367feac4c5cfa23eaa","tid":654562,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T18:16:25.000Z","msg":"要完始終會完<br />\n<br />\n未完之前會認真投入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbb023d1948f59dec6384f488a7603c3f8f7d22","tid":654562,"uid":183722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T18:21:25.000Z","msg":"用啲時間培養下感情同安全感 時間會證明一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9902ebd98abe4b0932d0ae7aefce06c29019bfb","tid":654562,"uid":48222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T18:25:44.000Z","msg":"重傷過兩次<br />\n依家有人追都唔敢開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf823be3aa7158effe904506da2416a7da6df8b6","tid":654562,"uid":40010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T18:26:43.000Z","msg":"曾經受過傷，仲要好傷<br />\n但宜家已經有更好嘅愛情<br />\n覺得之前嘅經歷係種體驗<br />\n雖然會有可惜，但係已經唔痛<br />\n因為每段感情都唔同<br />\n時間可以令你放低一齊<br />\n放眼未來，搵你嘅真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b424bd00cec1c221b4baacaeea82ad99197af33","tid":654562,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T21:00:40.000Z","msg":"覺得投放咁多心機落去 可能空手而回<br />\n所以決定愛自己多啲 起碼自己唔會離開自己"}]}